284
00:34:06,120 --> 00:34:12,630
♪Singing joys and sorrows to the skies♪

285
00:34:12,630 --> 00:34:15,830
♪I stand in the heart of these lands♪

286
00:34:15,830 --> 00:34:19,140
♪My shadow bears no crown or robe♪

287
00:34:19,390 --> 00:34:25,160
♪Then I know truth needs no disguise♪

288
00:34:25,550 --> 00:34:28,810
♪The green hills see me as I am♪

289
00:34:28,810 --> 00:34:32,030
♪Like dew, lightning,
and moon on the river♪

290
00:34:32,530 --> 00:34:38,230
♪Showing me exactly who I am♪

291
00:34:54,060 --> 00:34:57,980
(Ningzhou County Qinqiang Opera Troupe's
Yang Men Nyu Jiang was a hit)

292
00:34:57,980 --> 00:35:02,820
(Tomb of Gou Cunzhong,
erected by all of Ningzhou County)

293
00:35:02,840 --> 00:35:04,320
Today is your first seventh-day.

294
00:35:05,120 --> 00:35:06,200
We came to see you.

295
00:35:08,320 --> 00:35:09,160
Cunzhong,

296
00:35:10,920 --> 00:35:11,800
we

297
00:35:12,600 --> 00:35:14,160
can only go with you this far.

298
00:35:15,400 --> 00:35:16,440
Don't be afraid.

299
00:35:17,440 --> 00:35:19,160
(Tomb of Gou Cunzhong)
With Master

300
00:35:19,160 --> 00:35:20,200
and the brothers there,

301
00:35:20,880 --> 00:35:21,920
you won't be lonely.

302
00:35:23,120 --> 00:35:24,080
When you see them,

303
00:35:25,160 --> 00:35:26,320
greet them for us.

304
00:35:31,120 --> 00:35:32,120
What should we do?

305
00:35:35,480 --> 00:35:36,760
I'm leaving tomorrow.

306
00:35:40,120 --> 00:35:42,240
It's time for us to bow out.

307
00:35:43,680 --> 00:35:44,520
Master,

308
00:35:44,920 --> 00:35:46,080
where are you going?

309
00:35:49,000 --> 00:35:50,080
To the provincial troupe.

310
00:35:50,680 --> 00:35:52,720
They're rehearsing old plays too.

311
00:35:53,000 --> 00:35:55,440
They asked me to be a consultant.

312
00:35:56,840 --> 00:35:58,160
Will you tell Zhu Jiru?

313
00:35:59,080 --> 00:35:59,920
No.

314
00:36:00,800 --> 00:36:01,840
I'm not telling anyone.

315
00:36:02,120 --> 00:36:02,960
I won't trouble them.

316
00:36:04,680 --> 00:36:06,000
You're always so carefree.

317
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:09,160
The world is boundless.

318
00:36:09,960 --> 00:36:11,480
Everything has its time.

319
00:36:13,640 --> 00:36:15,520
Those meant to leave have left.

320
00:36:17,520 --> 00:36:18,560
From now on, the stage

321
00:36:20,040 --> 00:36:21,040
is all yours.

322
00:36:24,800 --> 00:36:25,920
You must keep singing.

323
00:36:27,440 --> 00:36:28,280
However hard it gets,

324
00:36:29,240 --> 00:36:30,440
you have to keep singing.

325
00:36:30,440 --> 00:36:35,140
(Tomb of Gou Cunzhong,
erected by all of Ningzhou County)

326
00:37:30,400 --> 00:37:43,360
♪Li Lanying honors the loyal souls♪

327
00:37:45,680 --> 00:37:59,640
♪Witnessed by heaven and earth♪

328
00:38:13,100 --> 00:38:17,380
(Grand Auditorium, Weimin General Store)

329
00:38:17,400 --> 00:38:18,880
(Gu Cunxiao left.)

330
00:38:19,440 --> 00:38:21,840
(Zhou Cunren moved
to the Bureau of Culture.)

331
00:38:22,360 --> 00:38:24,440
(Qiu Cunyi returned to his hometown.)

332
00:38:25,440 --> 00:38:26,760
(Yi Qing'e watched them)

333
00:38:26,760 --> 00:38:28,440
(leave one after another,)

334
00:38:28,840 --> 00:38:31,440
(feeling a deep void in her heart.)

335
00:38:32,680 --> 00:38:33,680
(These four old men)

336
00:38:33,880 --> 00:38:36,640
(rescued her from the kitchen stove)

337
00:38:37,240 --> 00:38:40,080
(and devoted their lives
to teaching her.)

338
00:38:41,040 --> 00:38:43,080
(Weimin General Store)
(Now, with them gone,)

339
00:38:43,080 --> 00:38:46,320
(the Cunjia Troupe
only has the name left.)

340
00:38:46,760 --> 00:38:48,320
(She fears that in this troupe,)

341
00:38:49,080 --> 00:38:50,880
(she'll be the only one left.)

342
00:38:50,880 --> 00:38:52,880
Ningzhou People's Broadcasting Station.

343
00:38:53,400 --> 00:38:54,920
We now bring you

344
00:38:55,080 --> 00:38:58,080
an important report from Beishan.

345
00:38:58,440 --> 00:39:01,840
Warm congratulations

346
00:39:01,840 --> 00:39:04,586
to Yang Men Nyu Jiang,
a newly adapted traditional opera,

347
00:39:04,646 --> 00:39:06,429
from Ningzhou County
Qinqiang Opera Troupe,

348
00:39:06,600 --> 00:39:09,480
on the great success

349
00:39:09,840 --> 00:39:11,760
in the Beishan arts showcase.

350
00:39:11,960 --> 00:39:14,200
It's also won
the Best Traditional Opera Award.

351
00:39:14,200 --> 00:39:16,060
Good for you, Troupe Leader.

352
00:39:16,060 --> 00:39:18,230
- Leaders and regional experts
- Listen!

353
00:39:18,560 --> 00:39:20,440
- who watched the show
- We won!

354
00:39:20,800 --> 00:39:24,040
highly praised the performance

355
00:39:24,040 --> 00:39:26,760
of Yang Men Nyu Jiang

356
00:39:27,000 --> 00:39:29,080
from the Ningzhou County Troupe.

357
00:39:30,360 --> 00:39:31,880
Everyone agreed

358
00:39:32,160 --> 00:39:33,480
that this is a rare, outstanding

359
00:39:33,680 --> 00:39:37,560
Qinqiang opera in our region

360
00:39:37,760 --> 00:39:40,360
and even the province.

361
00:39:40,720 --> 00:39:42,200
Hurry, hurry!

362
00:39:42,200 --> 00:39:43,040
What's the rush?

363
00:39:43,040 --> 00:39:44,200
Stop chopping! Stop!

364
00:39:44,466 --> 00:39:45,480
- What's wrong?
- Listen!

365
00:39:45,480 --> 00:39:46,400
- Yi Qing'e
- Listen!

366
00:39:46,680 --> 00:39:47,920
also won the First Prize

367
00:39:47,920 --> 00:39:50,680
for Young Actors.

368
00:39:51,960 --> 00:39:53,760
The play Yang Men Nyu Jiang

369
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:55,560
is a very difficult one.

370
00:39:55,560 --> 00:39:57,080
- They mean Laidi!
- Who else?

371
00:39:57,480 --> 00:39:58,360
Where is she?

372
00:39:58,360 --> 00:39:59,280
She's feeding the pigs.

373
00:39:59,280 --> 00:40:00,760
Hurry! Hurry up! Let's go!

374
00:40:01,080 --> 00:40:02,200
- Laidi!
- Laidi!

375
00:40:02,200 --> 00:40:03,480
Laidi!

376
00:40:04,240 --> 00:40:05,120
Laidi, hurry!

377
00:40:05,400 --> 00:40:06,240
Stop it!

378
00:40:06,440 --> 00:40:07,640
Stop feeding them! Hurry!

379
00:40:07,640 --> 00:40:08,920
You won an award! You won!

380
00:40:08,920 --> 00:40:10,440
First prize, Laidi!

381
00:40:10,940 --> 00:40:11,880
Stop calling her Laidi.

382
00:40:11,880 --> 00:40:13,880
It's Yi Qing'e now.

383
00:40:14,640 --> 00:40:15,640
You're on the radio!

384
00:40:15,640 --> 00:40:16,880
- Give it to me!
- Let's go!

385
00:40:16,880 --> 00:40:17,880
That's you. Go listen!

386
00:40:17,880 --> 00:40:18,666
I'll do it.

387
00:40:18,677 --> 00:40:19,840
Let's go listen to the radio!

388
00:40:19,840 --> 00:40:21,640
Her showcase after years of training

389
00:40:22,760 --> 00:40:24,320
was a complete success.

390
00:40:25,560 --> 00:40:26,800
You two are so lucky

391
00:40:26,800 --> 00:40:28,480
to be fed by the lead.

392
00:40:28,480 --> 00:40:30,280
We'll kill you to feed the lead.

393
00:40:31,400 --> 00:40:32,240
Eat up now.

394
00:40:32,240 --> 00:40:33,080
(Hot water)

395
00:40:33,080 --> 00:40:34,040
Reports say

396
00:40:34,440 --> 00:40:36,360
that at 11, Yi Qing'e

397
00:40:36,480 --> 00:40:39,320
joined Ningzhou County
Qinqiang Opera Troupe.

398
00:40:39,520 --> 00:40:42,040
Over the years in the trainee class,

399
00:40:42,240 --> 00:40:44,240
she feared no hardship or fatigue,

400
00:40:44,680 --> 00:40:47,280
practicing day after day,
year after year.

401
00:40:47,280 --> 00:40:49,040
- Do you hear that?
- She stayed disciplined

402
00:40:50,010 --> 00:40:51,900
and kept training her basic skills.

403
00:40:52,080 --> 00:40:53,030
Laidi!

404
00:40:53,480 --> 00:40:55,640
Stop working and listen to the radio!

405
00:40:55,640 --> 00:40:56,720
Don't walk away!

406
00:40:56,800 --> 00:40:58,760
Come listen! Stop working!

407
00:40:59,520 --> 00:41:00,570
Laidi!

408
00:41:01,060 --> 00:41:01,960
This silly girl.

409
00:41:01,960 --> 00:41:06,280
Our Ningzhou County
Qinqiang Opera Troupe

410
00:41:06,490 --> 00:41:10,280
trained such an excellent young actress.

411
00:41:10,870 --> 00:41:12,360
That's not fair.

412
00:41:12,880 --> 00:41:14,320
It was everyone's effort.

413
00:41:14,320 --> 00:41:15,800
Why does she get all the credit?

414
00:41:16,120 --> 00:41:17,620
Exactly.

415
00:41:18,300 --> 00:41:20,440
It is also very well executed.

416
00:41:21,770 --> 00:41:24,160
- Awesome!
- Qinqiang opera...

417
00:41:25,480 --> 00:41:27,290
Awesome!

418
00:41:27,900 --> 00:41:29,520
- Awesome.
- represents our heart.

419
00:41:29,640 --> 00:41:31,640
Come here. I need to talk to you.

420
00:41:44,480 --> 00:41:45,800
What's wrong? What is it?

421
00:41:48,840 --> 00:41:49,760
I'm being transferred.

422
00:41:50,920 --> 00:41:51,890
Where to?

423
00:41:52,330 --> 00:41:53,200
The provincial troupe.

424
00:41:54,520 --> 00:41:56,120
They're recruiting young people now.

425
00:41:56,400 --> 00:41:58,520
Zhou Yuzhi's family
pulled strings for her.

426
00:41:58,600 --> 00:41:59,480
She's leaving too.

427
00:42:01,140 --> 00:42:02,050
That's a good thing.

428
00:42:02,480 --> 00:42:04,880
It's the Tian'anmen of Qinqiang opera.

429
00:42:05,040 --> 00:42:05,930
You should go too.

430
00:42:06,120 --> 00:42:07,010
Let's go together.

431
00:42:07,640 --> 00:42:08,600
Me? I...

432
00:42:08,646 --> 00:42:09,805
I don't have the connections.

433
00:42:09,816 --> 00:42:10,960
I'm not going to daydream.

434
00:42:11,480 --> 00:42:12,640
I talked to my dad.

435
00:42:13,200 --> 00:42:14,400
He'll transfer you too.

436
00:42:15,070 --> 00:42:16,080
I'm not going.

437
00:42:17,800 --> 00:42:18,880
Are you going to stay

438
00:42:20,480 --> 00:42:22,520
in this valley forever for her?

439
00:42:28,866 --> 00:42:30,066
I'm not doing this for anyone.

440
00:42:35,670 --> 00:42:36,530
Listen to me.

441
00:42:37,200 --> 00:42:38,760
Or your life will be ruined,

442
00:42:39,600 --> 00:42:40,920
just like Master Gou.

443
00:42:47,560 --> 00:42:48,420
Thank you.

444
00:42:49,140 --> 00:42:50,070
I mean it.

445
00:42:52,160 --> 00:42:53,233
I wish you a bright future.

446
00:43:05,020 --> 00:43:06,940
=The Lead=
(Preview)

447
00:43:09,240 --> 00:43:11,800
I'm representing the County CPPCC today

448
00:43:11,800 --> 00:43:13,280
to share some good news.

449
00:43:13,480 --> 00:43:14,930
They made me a CPPCC Member.

450
00:43:15,200 --> 00:43:16,110
What?

451
00:43:16,280 --> 00:43:17,480
You'll be my boss from now on.

452
00:43:17,480 --> 00:43:19,160
Hey, why are you joking with the kid?

453
00:43:19,406 --> 00:43:20,706
She's now famous all over Beishan

454
00:43:20,717 --> 00:43:22,209
as the Little Queen of Qinqiang Opera.

455
00:43:22,220 --> 00:43:23,080
Yi Qing'e.

456
00:43:23,080 --> 00:43:26,880
I took these photos of you
with color film.

457
00:43:26,880 --> 00:43:27,790
Every single one is...

458
00:43:27,820 --> 00:43:29,420
This is a dressing room, not a commune.

459
00:43:29,420 --> 00:43:30,360
Get out.

460
00:43:30,390 --> 00:43:31,550
You did it on purpose!

461
00:43:31,550 --> 00:43:32,720
- That's right!
- You...

462
00:43:37,000 --> 00:43:41,620
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

463
00:43:43,090 --> 00:43:47,930
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

464
00:43:49,370 --> 00:43:53,560
♪We met and brushed past♪

465
00:43:55,120 --> 00:44:02,420
♪Your shadow drifted out of sight♪

466
00:44:16,790 --> 00:44:20,540
♪The stove fire blazed in my dream♪

467
00:44:22,140 --> 00:44:27,710
♪Lit up the tracks of pearly tears♪

468
00:44:28,830 --> 00:44:32,890
♪In my dream, water sleeves flew♪

469
00:44:34,020 --> 00:44:39,610
♪Hiding a lifetime of love♪

470
00:44:40,770 --> 00:44:44,970
♪The Qinling Mountains
crossed the stage♪

471
00:44:46,010 --> 00:44:51,640
♪Spring water brewed strong wine♪

472
00:44:52,810 --> 00:44:57,500
♪Sheep moved through the valley♪

473
00:44:58,180 --> 00:45:03,350
♪It felt like a promise
from another life♪

474
00:45:04,020 --> 00:45:09,050
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

475
00:45:10,080 --> 00:45:15,510
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

476
00:45:15,890 --> 00:45:21,170
♪If I chose again, I'd still roam♪

477
00:45:22,120 --> 00:45:27,930
♪All over this sunlit plateau♪

478
00:45:27,930 --> 00:45:33,350
♪The dream ends; the curtain falls♪

479
00:45:33,900 --> 00:45:39,410
♪Moonlight washes off this stage makeup♪

480
00:45:39,960 --> 00:45:44,920
♪The one in the mirror wears gray hair♪

481
00:45:45,940 --> 00:45:51,220
♪Already sang all my joy and sorrow♪

482
00:45:52,020 --> 00:46:01,050
♪Already shouted across Qinchuan Plain♪

